    "Background": {
      "text": "Occurs via direct blow to thumb or dorsiflexion and radial deviation force\nMajor complication is nonunion",
      "subsections": {},
      "tables": [],
      "links": []
    },
    "Clinical_Features": {
      "text": "Painful thumb movement\nWeak pinch\nTTP at apex of anatomic snuffbox, base of thenar eminence",
